<paragraph id="8BB636D20969FFA32AD651ABFECAFAB9" blockId="11.[151,1437,1087,1401]" pageId="11" pageNumber="512">
Original reference: Guérin-Méneville (1842) (as 
<taxonomicName id="4C094D510969FFA328F851ABFBBFFA84" box="[745,1078,1267,1293]" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Eriopis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="512" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="opposita" subGenus="Hippodamia">
